        <body>
            <div1 xml:id="d001" type="work" decls="#md" met="H">
                <head>
                    <title>1</title>
                    <bibl source="digital">Cristina Zanatta</bibl>
                </head>
                <l xml:id="d001l1" n="1">Languent acephali fratres pro re spiritali,</l>
                <l xml:id="d001l2" n="2">Pro patre uitali, pro patrono generali,</l>
                <l xml:id="d001l3" n="3">Non reminiscuntur, quia multi multa loquntur,</l>
                <l xml:id="d001l4" n="4">Et male dicuntur, quia proprium uelle sequntur.</l>
                <l xml:id="d001l5" n="5">Cumpromissorum ruptores, causa dolorum,</l>
                <l xml:id="d001l6" n="6">Accipient alapam, quia nolunt condere papam.</l>
                <l xml:id="d001l7" n="7">Non concordamus, nec concordare putamus,</l>
                <l xml:id="d001l8" n="8">Et tamen hic stamus, cum nil pietatis agamus,</l>
                <l xml:id="d001l9" n="9">Ut consumamus nos insimul et pereamus,</l>
                <l xml:id="d001l10" n="10">Quod non curamus de fama, quam lapidamus,</l>
                <l xml:id="d001l11" n="11">Nec bene pensamus de mundo, quem laniamus.</l>
                <l xml:id="d001l12" n="12">Ergo seruamus nos ipsos et faciamus,</l>
                <l xml:id="d001l13" n="13">Quod non perdamus haec tempora, nec tepeamus.</l>
                <l xml:id="d001l14" n="14">Quem formidamus occasum, preueniamus.</l>
                <l xml:id="d001l15" n="15">Sponsum condamus, quem sponse preficiamus.</l>
                <l xml:id="d001l16" n="16">Compromittendo uel scrutineum faciendo</l>
                <l xml:id="d001l17" n="17">Conditione pari consueuit papa creari.</l>
                <l xml:id="d001l18" n="18">Set compromissum iam rumpitur illico scissum,</l>
                <l xml:id="d001l19" n="19">Et de scrutineo non confidas bene fio!</l>
                <l xml:id="d001l20" n="20">Amodo quid restat? Nichil inspiracio prestat.</l>
                <l xml:id="d001l21" n="21">Uulgi, stante nola, restat, uexacio sola.</l>
                <l xml:id="d001l22" n="22">Pone, quod artentur, et eis alimenta negentur,</l>
                <l xml:id="d001l23" n="23">Ac si sic fieret electio, facta ualeret.</l>
                <l xml:id="d001l24" n="24">Si sequimur iura, non est umquam ualitura.</l>
                <l xml:id="d001l25" n="25">Tempus tremestre lapsum per transtra fenestre</l>
                <l xml:id="d001l26" n="26">Nos uetat eligere, dicens hec iura iubere.</l>
                <l xml:id="d001l27" n="27">Nam ius translatum per Christi pontificatum</l>
                <l xml:id="d001l28" n="28">Non cancellatum remanebit uel uiolatum.</l>
                <l xml:id="d001l29" n="29">Nos expectantes feriamus nil operantes,</l>
                <l xml:id="d001l30" n="30">Donec de celis mictatur papa fidelis.</l>
                <l xml:id="d001l31" n="31">Tres uoces desunt hiis qui per nomina praesunt.</l>
                <l xml:id="d001l32" n="32">Qui regnare uolunt, has uoces addere nolunt.</l>
                <l xml:id="d001l33" n="33">Set non regnabunt, nec papam dimidiabunt,</l>
                <l xml:id="d001l34" n="34">Et sic papatus per eos remanet uiduatus.</l>
                <l xml:id="d001l35" n="35">Mansio pulcra satis et copia fertilitatis</l>
                <l xml:id="d001l36" n="36">Fratribus artatis adsunt diffidere paratis.</l>
                <l xml:id="d001l37" n="37">Quod nocet artatis patrem subducere natis,</l>
                <l xml:id="d001l38" n="38">Disce quod enim natis nocuit differre paratis.</l>
                <l xml:id="d001l39" n="39">Est pudor inde satis patris de morte creatis;</l>
                <l xml:id="d001l40" n="40">Impedit illatis papam recreare uocatis.</l>
                <l xml:id="d001l41" n="41">Qui clausi statis, qui pinguia queque uoratis,</l>
                <l xml:id="d001l42" n="42">Cum bene papatis, papam fecisse putatis.</l>
                <l xml:id="d001l43" n="43">Hoc puerile satis, quia litora bubus aratis,</l>
                <l xml:id="d001l44" n="44">Uentribus inflatis, tunc numina ceca creatis.</l>
                <l xml:id="d001l45" n="45">Hec mea prediri uerba notate uiri,</l>
                <l xml:id="d001l46" n="46">Turpiter inclusi tituloque pudoris abusi:</l>
                <l xml:id="d001l47" n="47">Ut decet acephalos, tres ludi sumite talos.</l>
                <l xml:id="d001l48" n="48">Uos qui papari uultis honore pari,</l>
                <l xml:id="d001l49" n="49">Mittite taxillos; dabitur fortasse per illos</l>
                <l xml:id="d001l50" n="50">Uobis patronus, uir sacer atque bonus.</l>
                <l xml:id="d001l51" n="51">Sors dat machiam, nec erit mirabile, si iam</l>
                <l xml:id="d001l52" n="52">Dat papam uobis tessara iuncta globis.</l>
                <l xml:id="d001l53" n="53">Est festinandum uobis ad pontificandum.</l>
                <l xml:id="d001l54" n="54">Nam formidandus uenit Octo magnificandus;</l>
                <l xml:id="d001l55" n="55">Augebit numerum facie de semine serum.</l>
                <l xml:id="d001l56" n="56">Sero detur ei, si laus sit digna diei.</l>
                <l xml:id="d001l57" n="57">Nec Ior nec danus corruptor cotidianus,</l>
                <l xml:id="d001l58" n="58">Nec Gaietanus indagator male sanus,</l>
                <l xml:id="d001l59" n="59">Non potuere dare papam nec dimidiare.</l>
                <l xml:id="d001l60" n="60">Ignis de celo cursu descendat an&lt;h&gt;elo,</l>
                <l xml:id="d001l61" n="61">Et feriat telo fratres qui sunt sine zelo.</l>
                <l xml:id="d001l62" n="62">Fratres discordes faciat deus esse uecordes,</l>
                <l xml:id="d001l63" n="63">Nisi sint concordes, &lt;h&gt;os fedant undique sordes.</l>
            </div1>
